io.straas.android.sdk.circall

Class CircallToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.straas.android.sdk.circall.CircallToken

  • public final class CircallToken
extends Object
    CircallToken represents a room CirCall token. You could put your token jwt in CircallToken(String) to get the CircallToken representing a room CirCall token.
    See Also:
    CirCall token
